summary: idc what anyone says. rapline are the most diverse rappers out there in the korean music industry. those khiphop wannabes don’t...
body: idc what anyone says. rapline are the most diverse rappers out there in the korean music industry. those khiphop wannabes don’t even stand a chance to them, and they’re always trying to drag bts down. bts has proven time and time again that their lyrics, the ways they switch up their flow, and the beats/instrumentals they incorporate are always god tier. it’s extremely hard for others to compete. can they compete w/ namjoon’s lyricism? his witty wordplays? can they compete w/ yoongi’s different rap styles and flows? can they compete w/ hobi’s trap style, beat riding rap? nah, i don’t think they can 🤧 for real tho, try putting rapline in a ring full of khiphop rappers and see who wins. i honestly want to see this happen lol.

body:
Live and Love.

You may feel like you’re worthless in this world but trust me you dont need to be a super hero and save someone from burning fire, feed every poor hubgry soul to prove your worth in tgis world. God created everything and everyone for a reason . yours could be to feed a stary cat, remove a peice of glass from way so nobody gets hurt, free a bird that’s trapped in a room woth no open window, help an old man cross the road , help a pregnant woman carry something, show way to a lost traveler and so much more is there i this world you can do that can prove that yout life is worth living and if you still feel like you’re not enough for everyone then always remember you’re your own very first priority, yyou should love yourself above all and everyone, if you dont have enough love for yourself how will you give it to others and how much ?? Life is beautiful and worth living, it may not seem like it from your view but try to see it from someone else’ eyes for once maybe you wi find a reason to live nd a reason to LOVE.
